<ul class="project-title-and-text">
    <li class="project-title">
        Emmelina
    </li>

    <li class="project-type">
        Brand Identity
    </li>

    <li class="project-tools">
        Photoshop, Figma, CapCut
    </li>

    <li class="project-objective-title">
        About
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text">
        Emmelina is a dairy brand built around a single illustrative mark: a cow face that does the heavy lifting,
        keeping the logo itself clean and uncluttered. The color palette is grounded in the science of milk: yellow from
        the carotenoids naturally present in dairy, blue from the way light scatters through milk particles. The pattern
        on the business cards gives the brand a second visual register, adding energy without competing with the mark.
    </li>

</ul>

